INEX | Hush Pocket Rig | Pink
attributes.body:
The Inex Hush Pocket Rig is a versatile multi-purpose product. This item can be used as a concentrate rig, flower bubbler, and a roll up (cone/blunt) bubbler. The Pocket Rig has both a threaded mouth piece and 10mm female joint. The threaded features make the item incredibly convenient to travel with since you can leave the water in there while also making is smell resistant. This piece has a curved pierced diffuser pointing forward towards the inner curvature. This style of diffuser is easy to clean while at the same time providing an incredibly smooth hit for both flower and concentrate consumers. The function is set up to create a wave towards the front which prevents any splash back from hitting the user.

This Item Includes a bowl and a banger.

attributes.name: OLA | Vaporizer
attributes.body:
The vapor from your herbs, waxes, and even your favorite vape cartridges gather in this vaporizer's glass bowl. Once filled, grab the glass and tip it back to sip on the vapor. Hidr 8's Ola is a stunning cross between a Puffco Peak and a Volcano and it hits like a dream! 

The portable, travel-friendly Hidr 8 Ola features a 510 threaded connection inside that accepts many 510 threaded cartridges. This vaporizer is super simple to use. Just tap the power button on the front to turn the unit on then choose the voltage setting you want (yellow 2.5v, blue 3.0v, green 3.5v, red 4.0v) or enable the 30-second auto fill feature.

The Hidr 8 ola's "fill it up and tip it back" method of vaping allows you to unwind and vape at whatever tempo you like. You can tip the glass beaker back a little or as much as you prefer, making this vaporizer a joy to use minus any pressure to inhale all the vapor in one big draw. 

This innovative tabletop vaporizer is powered by a 1600mAh battery. It's a durable little vaporizer that looks nice. It's also a vaporizer you'll want to share with your friends so they can enjoy this new method of vaping herbs, waxes, and even their favorite 510 carts.
